description: Set years after the Dragon Wars which rendered the continent of Rakkon unfit for human habitation, Sehven lives a carefree life as a half-breed wheat thresher with his brother Clip. Seeking only to become a great dragonslayer in order to fulfill his lifelong dream, Sehven needs only to find a dragon to hunt, but in a time when dragons are thought to be long extinct, this proves to be much easier said than done. And then there's Leeka, Sehven's best friend and a self-proclaimed full-blooded dragon. But... if it's true, will Sehven be able to accomplish his goal through her?
name: Feather
